Undeads: Zombie, Skeleton
  mechanic: Firstly the enemyes are laying on the floor as corpses, after the player does any interaction in the room the corpses come to life and attack the player.

Bandits: Bandit, Fake trader
  mechanic: The trader is going to try scam the player. If the player left the room without noticeing the steal the trader will disapier, or the player can kill the trader for the stolen loot.

Elementals: Pille of stone with or withpout crystal
  mechanic: In a room there are some pile of stone. If the player try to break down the crystal from the stone the earth elementals come to life and attack the player.

Demons: Imp, Cambion

Devils: Succubus
  mechanic: The succubus tries to charm the character as a human.

